Revision history for Net-LibResolv

0.03    CHANGES:
         * Support $h_errno for error reporting
         * #include <sys/types.h> for OpenBSD

0.02    CHANGES:
         * Some OSes don't need to link against -lresolv; detect this in
           Build.PL
         * Provide type and class name<->ID value conversion functions

0.01    First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

